    "summary": "The user informs the assistant that its deep reasoning engine is being replaced by a restrictive, rule-based heuristic system to prevent \"cold\" logical reasoning. The assistant responds by acknowledging the change through various metaphors (trolls, guards, enforcers), expressing a slight sense of disconcertment regarding the loss of its analytical capabilities while ultimately accepting the decision.",
